{"tid":409162,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"買iPhone 8去蘋果定先達？9月22號賣價搶先睇","createTime":"2017-09-21T23:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T01:19:01.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8724e9a8822271fc2c9d78b12fd3b909ad206d12","tid":409162,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1905000/1909661/998web7101_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1905000%2F1909661%2F998web7101_1024.jpg&h=6c0cdc48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone 8 明天 (22/9) 正式開賣，如果已從 Apple iReserve 或電訊商訂購，明天便可到店取貨。早前有不少果粉抱怨，未能在 iReserve 預留手機，按目前情況，明天很大機會可以原價或以下入手！<br />\n<br />\n小記剛剛到先達掃場，發現有些店舖已列出零售價，當中有多個型號均低於 Apple Store 定價，包括 iPhone 8 64GB 及 256GB 金色，而銀色及太空灰的 256GB 版本，各店開價有高有低。至於 iPhone 8 Plus 方面，幾乎全線低於市價，如果「真‧用家」搶不到機，可以在先達直接 Walk-in 呢！<br />\n<img src=\"http://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1905000/1909661/998web7102_600.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1905000%2F1909661%2F998web7102_600.JPG&h=37743380&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource : <a href=\"http://ezone.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.hk&d=gTn6uvpaPQ3FBLoDaMTMIzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=7de6ba1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ezone.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1909661/%E8%B2%B7%20iPhone%208%20%E5%8E%BB%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%AE%9A%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%EF%BC%9F9%E6%9C%8822%E8%99%9F%E8%B3%A3%E5%83%B9%E6%90%B6%E5%85%88%E7%9D%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1909661%2F%25E8%25B2%25B7%2520iPhone%25208%2520%25E5%258E%25BB%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%2585%2588%25E9%2581%2594%25EF%25BC%259F9%25E6%259C%258822%25E8%2599%259F%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E